cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM 

This paper deals with image-to-image translation, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper introduces unsupervised attention mechanisms, which are a form of machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper also discusses the role of attention in human perception, which is related to graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
